gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 122, Raptors 99
gameRecap.excerpt: Victor Wembanyama led the Spurs with 27 points (10-14 FG), 14 rebounds, 10 blocks, five assists, and two steals as the Spurs defeated the Raptors, 122-99. Gradey Dick led the Raptors with 18 points. The Spurs move to 11-43 as the Raptors move to 19-35.
